{"tid":1544864,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人都肋間神經痛覺好煩","createTime":"2019-09-05T16:53:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T17:50:37.000Z","uid":293845,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"239f7a49afa6ea4aecd47059caab9e2b7db5686f","tid":1544864,"uid":293845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:53:48.000Z","msg":"有無人都有同樣問題，偶爾就突發性劇烈背痛肩痛，呼吸同一郁就更痛，難透氣咗人又虛弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇急症check X光又乜都睇唔出，醫院都係開一堆止痛藥同胃藥。中醫就話肝鬱脾虛引致脅痛，起碼有藥劑調理下咁。<br />\n<br />\n但其實即係中西醫都係無成因無得醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都係改變生活習慣嗰類廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「1、注意休息，避免可能使疼痛加重的影響因素。2、注意調整情緒，保持心情舒暢。3、注意保暖，避免受涼。」同服用止痛藥。中醫都係叮囑留意姿勢，心情嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁咪即係無得斷尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無啦啦某日就嚟一次料，咁狀態其實好麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  同樣問題嘅你地係點應對？有事就去開次藥？定我應該定期去中醫長期服藥調理落去？<br />\n<br />\n點先確保預防到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95d952e65998e171bbfa5c499585a17db201b90f","tid":1544864,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:54:37.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae6d72880bc3b64f25c7c020b9a4eeb58e24ce7f","tid":1544864,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:55:29.000Z","msg