/strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d97f7bb5858f45d603cc2e4cb06edde0ec0f31e","tid":1544864,"uid":126388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:00:22.000Z","msg":"同你一模一樣 經常係心口位置 你係咪都好瘦"},{"pid":"9f13d3dcbf0edbd9931e24d84330165f3b3c4a63","tid":1544864,"uid":293845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2d97f7bb5858f45d603cc2e4cb06edde0ec0f31e","tid":1544864,"uid":126388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:00:22.000Z","msg":"同你一模一樣 經常係心口位置 你係咪都好瘦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:05:16.000Z","msg":"yes！所以我當初以為心臟有事但原來唔係，都好彩嘅，但呢個病仲煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係啊成日俾人話好瘦，4x kg。"},{"pid":"ac49576342d6f7e4af32d67c4ec25a02799367c0","tid":1544864,"uid":28921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:31:59.000Z","msg":"我之前試過胸膜炎，係咪樓主講果d，成年先斷尾<br />\n果排成日痛覺得會無啦啦死左<br />\n睇左幾次醫生話因爲感冒菌未清走左去果度之類，都抵我死，成日唔食藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n提提大家，抗生素要依時服用"},{"pid":"86514662d4ab49b0d19ebf6ac54d9e4657ba4694","tid":1544864,"uid":126388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f13d3dcbf0edbd9931e24d84330165f3b3c4a63","tid":1544864,"uid":293845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2d97f7bb5858f