<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係啊成日俾人話好瘦，4x kg。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T22:46:46.000Z","msg":"有人同我講過係太瘦引致咁樣 一做操勞野就會發炎 我都試緊增肥睇下會唔會好啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T22:54:36.000Z","msg":"Impression <br />\nPneumonia <br />\nCostchondrites <br />\nPneumothorax <br />\nHeart failure <br />\n<br />\n有冇trauma? surgery?<br />\nFever?!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T23:11:53.000Z","msg":"全部都無 睇過兩次醫生都話肋骨發炎"},{"pid":"3f6f707067cdddfc8229b5e39f9058824b258f7d","tid":1544864,"uid":132461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T23:12:57.000Z","msg":"Your Chair Is Killing You...Time To Start Squatting.<br />\n<br />\nSitting Is Killing You Slowly<br />\n<br />\nYou'll probably be surprised at how much evidence there is out there that sitting is terrible for our bodies, and not just for our lower backs. Studies have shown over and over that sitting long periods of the day (as we almost all do) has disastrous effects our cellular and metabolic health.<br />\n<br />\nOur Bodies Were Not Designed To Sit<br />\n<br />\nThe Solution: Squatting<br />\n<br />\nIn most traditional cultures around the world, lower back pain is almost non-existent, despite the fact that people living in these societies perform a lot more physical labor.<br />\n<br />\nThe reason for this is pretty clear-cut. Most people in traditional societies rarely, if ever, sit in chairs for long periods of time. If they need to rest, they squat. Put simply, it's what our bodies are designed to do. <br />\n<br />\nWhen we squat, our lumbar spine extends, stretching the muscles in our low-back. There is little-to-no compression in the spine and stabilization is distributed between the muscles of the legs, hips and core. It's a perfect posture. <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://besynchro.com/blogs/blog/10612681-your-chair-is-killing-you-time-to-start-squatting\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbesynchro.com%2Fblogs%2Fblog%2F10612681-your-chair-is-killing-you-time-to-start-squatting&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWPhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=c8f99046\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://besynchro.com/blogs/blog/10612681-your-chair-is-killing-you-time-to-start-squatting</a>"},{"pid":"8c9e2d3236745067dfdcb9ebd68ae75f4cd891ae","tid":1544864,"uid":255450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T23:18:46.000Z","msg":"你睇下精神科，我叫呢種為焦累痛，要食抗抑鬱藥物先可以好架！"},{"pid":"9aeb8c21b1e46de363610932a45e9fc696abf44b","tid":1544864,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:15:02.000Z","msg":"試下食vitamin B complex,睇下可否緩解神經炎/神經痛"},{"pid":"64daf518ad81f3d892c900915250727415eb73c3","tid":1544864,"uid":293845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9aeb8c21b1e46de363610932a45e9fc696abf44b","tid":1544864,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:15:02.000Z","msg":"試下食vitamin B complex,睇下可否緩解神經炎/神經痛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:49:14.000Z","msg":"search咗下多到眼花撩亂，係咪是但一隻牌子就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8738e351b036c29911b527904402666676b61eb","tid":1544864,"uid":293845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c9e2d3236745067dfdcb9ebd68ae75f4cd891ae","tid":1544864,"uid":255450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T23:18:46.000Z","msg":"你睇下精神科，我叫呢種為焦累痛，要食抗抑鬱藥物先可以好架！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:50:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係掛即係我抑鬱不自知？我無唔開心喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}